node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Evan Tang in Singapore with @chichasanchen.sg. Image may contain: food

node.text:
Craving for @chichasanchen.sg?

They have collaborated with Yu Kee Duck Rice to offer islandwide delivery via GrabFood!

The duck rice was decent, and the bubble teas were excellent as usual!

I ordered my favourite Dong Ding Oolong Milk Tea, and Osmanthus Oolong with Mango 😍
I'm very tempted to order this now!
@im_alantam soon! Or u can order delivery 😊
Yes, I want the bubble milk tea! I haven't had one for weeks! Looking forward to getting one soon! 😁😁
Was talking abt chichasanchen with my extended family! Think i’m gonna order it tmr! 😀
Yass I want more bubble tea 😍🤗
Yaaaasssss my CHICHAAAAAA 😋😋 I've been craving them 😂
